## 3. Tech Stack

  Desktop shell:  Tauri 2 (Rust backend + OS-native webview)
  Frontend:       React 18 + TypeScript + Vite
  Styling:        Tailwind CSS utility classes + CSS custom properties
  State:          Zustand (one store per domain)
  Database:       SQLite via tauri-plugin-sql
  Config output:  Traefik v3 YAML (auto-generated, never hand-edited by user)
  Proxy daemon:   Traefik v3 (spawned and managed by Tauri)
  HA (optional):  keepalived VRRP for floating IP between two ProxyGate nodes

