## 11. Tauri Commands

proxy.rs:
  start_proxy(app: AppHandle)
  stop_proxy(app: AppHandle)
  reload_proxy(app: AppHandle)       SIGHUP on Linux, API call on Windows
  get_proxy_status()                 returns running bool + active route count

config.rs:
  write_config(yaml: String, path: String)
  get_config_path(app: AppHandle)
  validate_config(yaml: String)      runs traefik validate --configfile <tempfile>

health.rs:
  check_upstream_health(address: String) -> Result<u64, String>
    HTTP HEAD to http://{address}/health  returns latency ms or Err

logs.rs:
  start_log_tail(app: AppHandle)
    reads Traefik access log, emits Tauri events:
    app.emit_all("log-line", LogLine { timestamp, status, method, host, path, latency_ms })

certs.rs:
  list_certs(dir: String) -> Vec<CertInfo>
  upload_cert(domain: String, cert_pem: String, key_pem: String)
